The only thing to note is you still need to download a folder called "flash0" and place it in the "PSP" folder of this emulator. flash0 is easily found via web search and contains the original PSP text fonts. If you don't add this, certain games will have garbled or unreadable text. Lunar Silver Star Harmony and Growlanser had this problem, but now work perfectly with the flash0 folder added to the PSP folder. Highly recommended emulator overall.
